Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve found the Ajin, {\alpha&FF&}I need reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve found the Ajin, I need reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! {\alpha&FF&}Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve found the Ajin, near the Tsuki temple, \N{\alpha&FF&}I’ve found the Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve found the Ajin, near the Tsuki temple, \NI’ve found the Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The third Ajin in Japan has been discovered, at the moment he’s fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re underestimating your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an incident of national degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the double, {\alpha&FF&}no...  Triple the personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the double, no...  {\alpha&FF&}Triple the personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the double, no...  Triple the personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no doubt!{\alpha&FF&} He’s the Ajin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no doubt! He’s the Ajin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a hundred million!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They’ll really give it to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful with the Ajin’s voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve heard it puts you in some kind of paralysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and it gets impossible to move for a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! {\alpha&FF&}Can you stand up? Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Can you stand up? {\alpha&FF&}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Can you stand up? Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don’t die, then run over them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because people like you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because of you that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t move...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An Ajin is nothing more than\N a boring being that cannot die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to improve your\Nsenses and question what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When the privileges as an Ajin were given to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll show you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I came to save you, Tanaka-kun.
