Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The third Ajin found in Japan is still on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The news about the discovery of a new Ajin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3E2500&}They say he’s an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... It seems that we can get\N a lot of money if we catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}It’s morning already. \NAt this rate, they’ll end up finding us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}We have to hide while we can. \NWhen we get there, we’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hideout is an abandoned \Ncabin in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai likes using his motorcycle, \Nso he knows this kind of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go over there, we’ll be even-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But then... What will we do later on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,612.334)}The situation is worse than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,612.334)}All of Japan… No, all the people around the world must know of my existence at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,612.334)}There will be people all around the world trying to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re two, I’ll catch up to them quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,His accomplice is also a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be able to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they gotten any information?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They still haven’t finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, what’re you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll leave at this, for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You look really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to get a sincere answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel now? Knowing that your son is an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t thought my son... Wouldn’t be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a waste of time...\N {\alpha&FF&}How’s the search for Nagai Kei going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a waste of time...\N How’s the search for Nagai Kei going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman said she heard an Ajin’s scream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in one of the mountains on the way to Yamanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t think there would be witnesses this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His accomplice is most likely a novice, or a normal citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was a professional or an external agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it would have been impossible for them to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If he’s a novice that wants money,\N we’ll probably find him easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t think someone would help him for money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think someone would want to help an Ajin for something but money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,“Hat” has been seen near the household of the Nagai,\N communicate with the special squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“Hat” must be hunting down Nagai Kei, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s possible. Anyway, be careful at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We won’t follow him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst case-scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to avoid the worst of situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he hunts down Nagai Kei,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of innocent people will die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! He’s about to reach us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you use your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But there’s the noise of the motor, and also you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H302800&}We don’t have other choice.\N Although we don’t know if it’ll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If he falls, we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment. If I do it at this speed,\N that person will die...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn’t asked him for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This wouldn’t have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up! Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If only him didn’t exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai would be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If only him... {\alpha&FF&}If only him... If only him didn’t exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If only him... If only him... {\alpha&FF&}If only him didn’t exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If only him... If only him... If only him didn’t exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I faked I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn’t hurt at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll keep his motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can’t go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What’re you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My leg is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And with what just happened, it’s more than clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we’re together, you’ll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000028&}Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ajin and a human shouldn’t—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000022&}Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why, if you run away to a place\N no one knows, but me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you’ll still be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll patch you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve understood with the things that have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That I’m not... {\alpha&FF&}Human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That I’m not... Human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... {\alpha&FF&}It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if I tell him to leave me here, he wouldn’t listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With this leg I’ll put Kai in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do? {\alpha&FF&}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Think like one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an... Like an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an... Like an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei! {\alpha&FF&}Don’t–
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei! Don’t–
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, my leg is healed. Let’s go, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of a lot of people dying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe they want to avoid another Nakamura Shin’ya incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why they won’t take any big actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what will we do now, Satou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to show him the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll encounter Nagai Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... {\alpha&FF&}an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you’re okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What’re you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m more relaxed, and my head is alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H002407&}That’s not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H271800&}On the other side, you worry me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If a human dies, he cannot come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What’ll you do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If it’s on, it’ll give our location to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That doesn’t work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I would like to go somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you want to go somewhere safe,\N you need not to leave this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When food runs out, I’ll go for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If I recall correctly, the number of people\N disappeared last year was 2396.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}About 294 of them disappeared in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It was announced in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If every year, almost 300 people disappear in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}maybe they won’t find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If that’s the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But... {\alpha&FF&}We can’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But... We can’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to give away my peaceful\N style of life for being an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyuushu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My granpa lives in Kyuushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a village isolated from human contact,\N so no one is going to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even while being an Ajin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you’ll be able to live relaxed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that’s better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, it’s decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go buy some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I would like a tooth brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he hasn’t been around that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In this situation, doing things bigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,would be something risky for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H171F00&}I have that meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,People won’t stop complaining about money and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go here, {\alpha&FF&}I’ll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go here, I’ll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Act calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t say unnecessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A village in Kyuushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans that don’t get bothered by Ajins...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s impossible that humans like that exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, we still have 100 kilometers ahead of us.\N It will be impossible to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No only for an Ajin. It would be very dangerous for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it’s time to say goodbye to Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It’s time to say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, a detective came yesterday too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m from the Ajin’s Management Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The managing committee makes investigations on Ajin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and handles them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H00001E&}I don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m asking about the personal life of Nagai Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Be going through all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because you’re the sister of Nagai Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eriko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry to disturb you in this state, {\alpha&FF&}but I hope you can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry to disturb you in this state, but I hope you can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To know that a family member that I though was human was in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s too gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I... {\alpha&FF&}know someone who had\N an Ajin for family member.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I... know someone who had\N an Ajin for family member.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn’t know what that person felt like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonetheless,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want there to be more people\N like them, or like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because of that, that I want to clear some things out about the Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To know how they’re born,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to know if they’re truly immortal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and to know if they’re truly not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter if it’s insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing about your brother that called your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s something, not very important,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I tell you, you’ll go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Time ago...
