Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.37,Default - FSHBCK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.6\c&H263134&}Ghost?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.37,Default - FSHBCK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\blur0.6\shad0.8\4a&HFF&}Ghost?
