Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.04,Default - FSHBCK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\alpha&H80&\3c&HBCDEF5&}He’s coming out...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.04,Default - FSHBCK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.6\c&H263134&}He’s coming out...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.04,Default - FSHBCK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\blur0.6\shad0.8\4a&HFF&}He’s coming out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but he claimed there was a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai Kei said he saw the black ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t know if it was black or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san will get angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in those times,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2330,0,1,\c&HC1BEC0&\3c&HC1BEC0&\4c&HC1BEC0&)}Kei and me played a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the accomplice is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remembered something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how insignificant it is–
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What happe–?
